    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this car is in such incredible shape, you'd think it just rolled off the showroom floor today! It\u2019s been meticulously cared for, always garaged, and drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the sticker shock, this is the one for you. Come take a look\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
