    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade 2008 BMW M3 (E92) in Alpine White. This example features the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, delivering 414 hp with a stratospheric 8,400 RPM redline via eight individual throttle bodies. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for optimal power delivery. This mint specimen boasts a factory carbon fiber roof, lowering the center of gravity, and an unblemished Electronic Damper Control (EDC) system. Meticulously maintained with documented rod bearing service and a pristine subframe, this vehicle retains its original factory tolerances and structural rigidity. Performance is sharp, visceral, and mechanically flawless.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
