    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with a professional ceramic coating and absolutely zero rock chips or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is in a factory-fresh state, with the original leather aroma still present and zero signs of wear on the bolsters or controls. Mechanically, it is flawless; I have a complete binder of service records documenting every scheduled maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians. This car has never seen rain, let alone snow, and comes with all original keys, manuals, and a tailored premium cover. For the buyer who demands perfection, this is the one.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
