    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptional vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This unit remains in showroom condition, exhibiting a flawless exterior and an interior that retains its original factory freshness. Meticulously inspected and preserved, it offers an uncompromising driving experience for the discerning collector or enthusiast. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of such caliber.",
      "price": 48500.0,
