    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You seriously have to see this beauty to believe it! I\u2019ve taken incredible care of this car, and it honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Not a single scratch or dent, and the interior is absolutely spotless\u2014it even still has that new-car smell! It drives like an absolute dream and has been my pride and joy. I'm looking for someone who will love it just as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions! \u2728",
      "price": 43500.0,
