      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This specimen is a masterclass in mechanical preservation. Featuring a high-revving, naturally aspirated powerplant with a perfectly calibrated valvetrain, the throttle response remains razor-sharp across the entire powerband. The chassis exhibits zero torsional fatigue, supported by factory-spec subframe integrity and refreshed bushings that eliminate any lateral deflection. The limited-slip differential provides optimal torque vectoring, while the braking system retains its original bite with no evidence of thermal cycling on the rotors. Every fluid change has been documented, ensuring the internal tolerances of the transmission and engine remain within factory specifications. This is a true driver\u2019s car, free of the typical electronic gremlins or mechanical wear associated with its contemporaries.",
      "price": 46800.0,
